manifest.name: ExcaliBrain
manifest.description: A clean, intuitive and editable graph view for Obsidian
manifest.author: Zsolt Viczian

data.manifestValue: A clean, intuitive and editable graph view for Obsidian
data.communityListValue: ExcaliBrain is inspired by TheBrain and Breadcrumbs. It is an interactive, structured mind-map of your vault generated based on the folders and files in your vault by interpreting the links, Dataview fields, tags and YAML frontmatter in your Markdown files.
